race.comment: LONE FORCE (9) resumes here but the form he showed prior to the break was up to a race of this nature. Tuned up for this with two recent trials and maps ideally for this contest from gate two. Should be right there when the judge calls a halt. ECHO HUNTER (14) got a well-deserved victory last time out and will have derived a stack of confidence from that win. Is a three-time winner here and can make her presence felt. ROYAL GLADIATOR (18) has won over this track and trip and will be rock-hard fit for this. Worth serious consideration. RETAINER (13) hasn't been too far away in all three runs this campaign and looks one for the exotics players. ONE BEAT NO BEAT (2) best of the rest.
